  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in Senate",
    "asOf": "2022-03-16",
    "date": "2022-09-26T17:49:36Z",
    "text": "This bill revokes certain waivers of sanctions relating to Iran's nuclear activity, including for (1) the modernization or redesign of the Arak reactor, and (2) the preparation or modification of centrifuge cascades at the Fordow facility. The bill also prohibits the President from issuing a new waiver relating to such activities."
